original_title: Woman gone missing found dead in seas off Beruwala
original_body_lines: The body of a 25-year-old woman, who went missing two days ago, was found by a group of fishermen in the seas off ​​Beruwala.
The Beruwala police had received a complaint on Wednesday that the woman, Mohammad Faumin Shahnam Bhanu, a resident of Beruwala had gone missing.
Accordingly, a group of fishermen who went to sea from the Beruwala fishing pier this morning for fishing, found the body of the woman in the seas off two miles from the coast.
